parameters: \nc<>What... Why is the hideout like this...

\nc<>Oh, you're late, senpai. I've been waiting and getting
tired.
\nc<>Reina! Are you okay!! Did you get caught up in it?
\nc<>Wait a moment, Kei. Something seems strange.
\nc<>What are you talking about, Cashew Nut? It's Reina, right?

\nc<>Let's get out of here for now. We need to go look for
Candy--

\nc<>Oh, how dare you interfere in the affairs of a cat. But
even so, it won't change much.

\nc<>Oh, this is strange. Because Reina is just a normal
human... she shouldn't be able to do something like this...

\nc<>You were also looking for Candy and Sherbet, right? Don't
worry, I'm with both of them.

\nc<>Well, I can't really say that I'm doing well, though.
*laughs*
\nc<>...Lilith, what do you want to do?

\nc<>Oh, how unexpected. I thought you would be busy escaping
from reality for a while.

\nc<>It seems like you're not that surprised, huh? In fact, I
might be the one who got hurt.

\nc<>(Impossible! Reina is Lilith? I don't understand what's
going on.)
\nc<>(Honestly, I still think it's all a lie.)

\nc<>(But... the black magic, Candy and Sherbet behind me,
they're all real.)

\nc<>Severe wounds. If it stays like that, both of them might
become irreparable.

\nc<>In a situation like this... there's no way I can escape from
reality so carelessly...!
\nc<>Certainly, that's true. In any case, my goal is the same.
\nc<>Um... why are we doing this again?

\nc<>What do you think villains do when they catch someone
they're close to? It's obvious, they make them hostages.

\nc<>Please give up your magical girl powers and return to being
a normal human, senpai. Right now.
\nc<>If I do that, will you let those children go?

\nc<>No? I just need to borrow a little bit of magical girl power
there, so...
\nc<>Well, if you stay alive, I'll return the favor, okay?

\nc<>Why are you so angry? Senpai, you've been saying that you
want to quit this job for a long time, haven't you?
\nc<>Now is your chance, you know? It's not that difficult.

\nc<>If you just close your eyes and nod once, you can have the
normal life you've always wanted, you know?
\nc<>Of course, we will be friends for life

\nc<>Hehe. Are you saying that you don't intend to sacrifice
these children in order to obtain a happy life?

\nc<>While Senpai was struggling and taking a break from being a
magical girl, there were also others who went through
similarly difficult situations.

\nc<>What is the difference between those people and these
children? Oh, is it because they are cute girls after all?

\nc<>Shut up, shut up, shut up! There's no way I should be told
such things by you all!

\nc<>Ahaha! That's a valid point. Even if a villain talks about
good and evil, it just becomes a joke.

\nc<>So, if there's something you want, please grab it directly
with your own hands, Senpai. Just like always.
\nc<>(What should I do? What should I do? What should I do?)

\nc<>(If things continue like this, Candy and Sherbet will...),
(No, but where should I go...)

\nc<>They're not exactly unharmed, but they're pretty beat up...
They can still move somehow.

\nc<>There's only one place that seems to be the target for the
person who uses that black power, meow.

\nc<>Maybe other villains might be there too, meow. Let's prepare
as much as we can, meow.

\nc<>Understood. This time, I will definitely put an end to
it...!
\nc<>I obtained the memory R4: Succubus Queen.

\nc<>Good listeners increased by 7,000, and bad listeners
increased by 3,000.
